cs.DC, cs.NA, cs.SC, cs.DS, cs.MS

Reasoning: 
- cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) is the most likely category as the paper deals with communication reduction in distributed hierarchical N-Body algorithms. 
- cs.NA (Numerical Analysis) is also likely as the paper proposes strategies to improve partitioning and reduce communication in numerical algorithms. 
- cs.SC (Symbolic Computation and Formal Methods) is less likely but still possible as the paper may involve symbolic computations in the optimization of communication. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is also possible as the paper proposes modifications to existing algorithms to improve their performance. 
- cs.MS (Mathematical Software) is less likely but still possible as the paper may involve the development of software for implementing the proposed algorithms.
